    def display_help(self):
        print("""
ðŸ”¥ AVAILABLE LEARNING TOPICS:

ðŸ“š WEB SECURITY:
   â€¢ sql injection
   â€¢ xss / cross-site scripting
   â€¢ web application testing

ðŸŒ NETWORK SECURITY:
